# MemberController HTTP requests for VSCode REST Client (or similar)
# Base URL: http://localhost:8080
# Replace {{baseUrl}}, {{memberId}}, {{friendId}}, {{nickname}}, {{refreshToken}} with actual values or set them as environment variables.

### 회원 탈퇴 (requires Refresh token in Authorization header)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/members/{{memberId}}/resign
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### 상대방 정보 조회 (profile, lifestyle, preference)
GET {{baseUrl}}/members/8/information
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### 내 기본 프로필 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/members/{{memberId}}/basic
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### 내 LifeStyle 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/members/{{memberId}}/lifestyle
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### 내 Preference 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/members/{{memberId}}/preference
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### 내 프로필(기본) 수정 (EditMemberDTO)
POST {{baseUrl}}/members/{{memberId}}/editprofile
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "nickname": "jh_park",
